data.description: Ole Smith Farms Subdivision - Craftsman style 4 sides brick with board & baton, sits on a large lot .44 +/- of an acre. 4 bedroom 2 bath solid surface, great room, open floor plan, 1,859 +/- sq ft heated, plus 2 car garage, storm shelter in garage. covered front porch and back covered patio. 10' ceilings in living area, gas log fireplace, kitchen with an island and dining room, tile back splash, solid surface, pantry, state of the art LED under counter lighting, upgraded faucets & hardware. Flooring is Luxury vinyl plank, tile, upgraded carpet and 8 lb pad, carpet in bedrooms only, Master Suite, has walk-in closet, master bath with solid surfaces, two separate vanities, tiled walk in master shower and soaker tub. There are 2 linen closets and a coat closet.
